        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks to CD’s help Zoological Station has passed a crisis and is now flourishing.</p> 
<p>Is writing pamphlet on "the origin of vertebrates and the principle of succession of functions" [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">9991</hi> and <hi rend="doubleUnderline">10003</hi>]. It is likely CD will not be pleased with it, but he thinks he must now, after seven years, bring it out. Seeks to open the way for a new series of theoretical questions.</p> 
        </abstract>
